test_case_results.title: Page should consist of an HTML main heading element with "Coin Toss Game" as text content
Page should consist of an HTML paragraph element with "Heads (or) Tails" as text content
Page should initially consist of an HTML image element with alt attribute value as "toss result" and src attribute value as the URL for heads image
Page should consist of HTML button element with text content as "Toss Coin"
Page should initially consist of HTML paragraph element with text content as "Total: 0"
Page should initially consist of HTML paragraph element with text content as "Heads: 0"
Page should initially consist of HTML paragraph element with text content as "Tails: 0"
When the Toss Coin button is clicked, if the result is "heads" then the heads image should be displayed
When the Toss Coin button is clicked, if the result is "heads" then the heads count should be incremented by one
When the Toss Coin button is clicked, if the result is "tails" then the tails image should be displayed
When the Toss Coin button is clicked, if the result is "tails" then the tails count should be incremented by one
When the Toss Coin button is clicked, the total should be incremented by one
